The Music in Me



Jessica Terrill (Debbie Gibson) has made more than her share of sacrifices over the years, including forgoing her potential singing career to make room for her brother's and help her parents keep their family business afloat.

Although Jessica tries to keep her dreams tucked away, her friends and family push her to pursue them despite her protests. Fate steps in when the local church's choir director quits just weeks before the church's 100th anniversary celebration and Jessica is forced to revisit the dreams she left behind.




Original Air Date: 12-Apr-2015
